Paper: hep-th/9210070

Date: 1992-10-13

Title: On the Quantization of Reducible Gauge Systems

Authors: R. Ferraro, M. Henneaux and M. Puchin

Comments: 41 pages, Plain Tex file, ULB-PMIF\92-07, GTCRG/92-04

Journal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 34 (1993) 2757-2778

Reducible gauge theories with constraints linear in the momenta arequantized. The equivalence of the reduced phase space quantization, Diracquantization and BRST quantization is established. The ghosts of ghosts arefound to play a crucial role in the equivalence proof.